{"tid":516806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[兒子生性病] 仍有人留守公民廣場　政府對有人傷感遺憾籲盡快離開","createTime":"2018-01-01T17:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T17:43:04.000Z","uid":3628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e3cdce8bf360b39b3ba18235df645a17b248e6","tid":516806,"uid":3628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:24:46.000Z","msg":"民陣今發起元旦遊行，部分遊行人士於下午遊行後，進入政府總部東翼前地，至今仍有10多人於前地旗桿平台附近逗留。<br />\n<br />\n港府回應對有公眾集會者不遵守場地使用規則，及不聽從在場警務人員及保安人員指示，期間導致有人受傷及政府公物損壞表示遺憾，又指東翼前地開放作公眾集會的時間已結束，呼籲在場人士盡快離開。<br />\n<br />\n發言人重申，尊重市民依法享有的遊行及發表意見的權利，惟遊行及發表意見的權利並非沒有限制，有關人士必須遵守法律及相關使用規則，並避免對自身及其他人士構成危險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1980921/%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E3%80%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7%E6%84%9F%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE%E7%B1%B2%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1980921%2F%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7%25E6%2584%259F%25E9%2581%25BA%25E6%2586%25BE%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B&d=lnfHYMtKiWBkQNsoCebniqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=5014ab07\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1980921/%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E3%80%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7%E6%84%9F%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE%E7%B1%B2%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B</a>"},{"pid":"be83e42ce1016db97fa87dfc951a1e5c33a84200","tid":516806,"uid":3628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21dc50f102d96e73c8622f8f731145f2988a6492","tid":51